{"id":142,"ayahs":[{"number":111,"arabic":"۞ وَلَوْ أَنَّنَا نَزَّلْنَآ إِلَيْهِمُ ٱلْمَلَٰٓئِكَةَ وَكَلَّمَهُمُ ٱلْمَوْتَىٰ وَحَشَرْنَا عَلَيْهِمْ كُلَّ شَىْءٍۢ قُبُلًۭا مَّا كَانُوا۟ لِيُؤْمِنُوٓا۟ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ وَلَٰكِنَّ أَكْثَرَهُمْ يَجْهَلُونَ","translation":"And even if We were to send down angels unto them, and if the dead were to speak unto them and [even if] We were to assemble before them, face to face, all the things [that can prove the truth], they would still not believe unless God so willed But [of this] most of them are entirely unaware.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/900.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":74583,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَلَوْ","translation":"এবং যদি (হতো)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74584,"position":2,"arabic":"أَنَّنَا","translation":"যে আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74585,"position":3,"arabic":"نَزَّلْنَآ","translation":"আমরা অবতীর্ণ করতাম","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74586,"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِمُ","translation":"প্রতি তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74587,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةَ","translation":"ফেরেশতাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74588,"position":6,"arabic":"وَكَلَّمَهُمُ","translation":"এবং তাদের সাথে কথাও বলত","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74589,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْمَوْتَىٰ","translation":"মৃতরা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74590,"position":8,"arabic":"وَحَشَرْنَا","translation":"এবং আমরা একত্র করতাম","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74591,"position":9,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِمْ","translation":"সামনে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74592,"position":10,"arabic":"كُلَّ","translation":"সব","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74593,"position":11,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ","translation":"কিছুই","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74594,"position":12,"arabic":"قُبُلًۭا","translation":"সামনাসামনি","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74595,"position":13,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"(তবুও) না","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74596,"position":14,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","translation":"তারা ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74597,"position":15,"arabic":"لِيُؤْمِنُوٓا۟","translation":"যেন তারা ঈমান আনবে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74598,"position":16,"arabic":"إِلَّآ","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74599,"position":17,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74600,"position":18,"arabic":"يَشَآءَ","translation":"ইচ্ছে করতেন (তবে ভিন্ন কথা)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74601,"position":19,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74602,"position":20,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِنَّ","translation":"কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74603,"position":21,"arabic":"أَكْثَرَهُمْ","translation":"অধিকাংশই তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74604,"position":22,"arabic":"يَجْهَلُونَ","translation":"মূর্খতা করে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_111_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74605,"position":23,"arabic":"١١١","translation":"(১১১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":112,"arabic":"وَكَذَٰلِكَ جَعَلْنَا لِكُلِّ نَبِىٍّ عَدُوًّۭا شَيَٰطِينَ ٱلْإِنسِ وَٱلْجِنِّ يُوحِى بَعْضُهُمْ إِلَىٰ بَعْضٍۢ زُخْرُفَ ٱلْقَوْلِ غُرُورًۭا ۚ وَلَوْ شَآءَ رَبُّكَ مَا فَعَلُوهُ ۖ فَذَرْهُمْ وَمَا يَفْتَرُونَ","translation":"AND THUS it is that against every prophet We have set up as enemies the evil forces from among humans as well as from among invisible beings that whisper unto one another glittering half-truths meant to delude the mind But they could not do this unless thy Sustainer had so willed: stand, therefore, aloof from them and from all their false imagery!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/901.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":74781,"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এবং এভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74782,"position":2,"arabic":"جَعَلْنَا","translation":"আমরা বানিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74783,"position":3,"arabic":"لِكُلِّ","translation":"জন্যে প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74784,"position":4,"arabic":"نَبِىٍّ","translation":"নাবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74785,"position":5,"arabic":"عَدُوًّۭا","translation":"শত্রু","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74786,"position":6,"arabic":"شَيَـٰطِينَ","translation":"শয়তানদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74787,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسِ","translation":"(মধ্য হতে) মানুষের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74788,"position":8,"arabic":"وَٱلْجِنِّ","translation":"ও জিনদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74789,"position":9,"arabic":"يُوحِى","translation":"উস্কানি দিতে থাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74790,"position":10,"arabic":"بَعْضُهُمْ","translation":"কিছু অংশ তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74791,"position":11,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","translation":"প্রতি","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74792,"position":12,"arabic":"بَعْضٍۢ","translation":"(অন্য) কিছু অংশের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74793,"position":13,"arabic":"زُخْرُفَ","translation":"চাকচিক্য (দ্বারা)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74794,"position":14,"arabic":"ٱلْقَوْلِ","translation":"কথার","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74795,"position":15,"arabic":"غُرُورًۭا ۚ","translation":"ধোঁকার (উদ্দেশ্যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74797,"position":16,"arabic":"وَلَوْ","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74798,"position":17,"arabic":"شَآءَ","translation":"ইচ্ছে করতেন","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74799,"position":18,"arabic":"رَبُّكَ","translation":"তোমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74800,"position":19,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74801,"position":20,"arabic":"فَعَلُوهُ ۖ","translation":"তারা করতো তা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74803,"position":21,"arabic":"فَذَرْهُمْ","translation":"অতএব ছেড়ে দাও তাদেরকে (তাদের অবস্থায়)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74804,"position":22,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং যা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74805,"position":23,"arabic":"يَفْتَرُونَ","translation":"তারা রচনা করছে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_112_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74806,"position":24,"arabic":"١١٢","translation":"(১১২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":113,"arabic":"وَلِتَصْغَىٰٓ إِلَيْهِ أَفْـِٔدَةُ ٱلَّذِينَ لَا يُؤْمِنُونَ بِٱلْءَاخِرَةِ وَلِيَرْضَوْهُ وَلِيَقْتَرِفُوا۟ مَا هُم مُّقْتَرِفُونَ","translation":"Yet, to the end that the hearts of those who do not believe in the life to come might incline towards Him, and that in Him they might find contentment, and that they might earn whatever they can earn [of merit] -","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/902.mp3","surahId":6,"words":[{"id":75043,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلِتَصْغَىٰٓ","translation":"এবং (তারা এজন্যে করে) যেন ঝুঁকে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_113_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75044,"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِ","translation":"প্রতি তার (অর্থাৎ চাকচিক্যের)","audioUrl":"wbw/006_113_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75045,"position":3,"arabic":"أَفْـِٔدَةُ","translation":"(তাদের) অন্তর","audioUrl":"wbw/006_113_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75046,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_113_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75047,"position":5,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/006_113_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75048,"position":6,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"ঈমান আনে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_113_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75049,"position":7,"arabic":"بِٱلْـَٔاخِرَةِ","translation":"উপর আখিরাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/006_113_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75050,"position":8,"arabic":"وَلِيَرْضَوْهُ","translation":"এবং যেন তাতে তারা পরিতুষ্ট হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/006_113_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75051,"position":9,"arabic":"وَلِيَقْتَرِفُوا۟","translation":"এবং যেন তারা অপকর্ম করে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_113_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75052,"position":10,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_113_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75053,"position":11,"arabic":"هُم","translation":"তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/006_113_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75054,"position":12,"arabic":"مُّقْتَرِفُونَ","translation":"অপকর্ম করছে","audioUrl":"wbw/006_113_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":75055,"position":13,"arabic":"١١٣","translation":"(১১৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":114,"arabic":"أَفَغَيْرَ ٱللَّهِ أَبْتَغِى حَكَمًۭا وَهُوَ ٱلَّذِىٓ أَنزَلَ إِلَيْكُمُ ٱلْكِتَٰبَ مُفَصَّلًۭا ۚ وَٱلَّذِينَ ءَاتَيْنَٰهُمُ ٱلْكِتَٰبَ يَعْلَمُونَ أَنَّهُۥ مُنَزَّلٌۭ مِّن رَّبِّكَ بِٱلْحَقِّ ۖ فَلَا تَكُونَنَّ مِنَ ٱلْمُمْتَرِينَ","translation":"[say thou:] \"Am I, then, to look unto anyone but God for judgment [as